  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-5678-90ab-cdef-123456789012",
    "name": "NearProp - Subscription Management",
    "description": "# NearProp Subscription Management APIs\n\nThis collection contains endpoints for managing subscription plans, user subscriptions, and content visibility in the NearProp platform.\n\n## Admin Subscription Plan Management\nAllows administrators to create, update, and manage subscription plans with different features and pricing.\n\n## User Subscription Management\nEnables users to subscribe to plans, renew subscriptions, and manage their active subscriptions.\n\n## Payment Integration\nHandles payment processing through the Razorpay payment gateway, including payment initiation, verification, and refunds.\n\n## Content Visibility Control\nHandles automatic content hiding and deletion based on subscription status and plan settings.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
